import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

import seaborn as sns

%matplotlib inline
InÂ [2]:
df = pd.read_csv('train.csv')

df['pickup_datetime'] = df['pickup_datetime'].map(lambda x: pd.to_datetime(x, format='%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'))
df['dropoff_datetime'] = df['dropoff_datetime'].map(lambda x: pd.to_datetime(x, format='%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S'))

df['pickup_hour'] = df['pickup_datetime'].map(lambda x: x.hour)
df['pickup_dayofweek'] = df['pickup_datetime'].map(lambda x: x.dayofweek)
df['dropoff_hour'] = df['dropoff_datetime'].map(lambda x: x.hour)
df['dropoff_dayofweek'] = df['dropoff_datetime'].map(lambda x: x.dayofweek)

allLat = np.array(list(df['pickup_latitude']) + 
                     list(df['dropoff_latitude']))
allLong = np.array(list(df['pickup_longitude']) +
                      list(df['dropoff_longitude']))

longLimits = [np.percentile(allLong, 0.3), 
              np.percentile(allLong, 99.7)]
latLimits = [np.percentile(allLat, 0.3),
             np.percentile(allLat, 99.7)]
durLimits = [np.percentile(df['trip_duration'], 0.4),
             np.percentile(df['trip_duration'], 99.7)]

df = df[(df['pickup_latitude']   >= latLimits[0] ) & (df['pickup_latitude']   <= latLimits[1]) ]
df = df[(df['dropoff_latitude']  >= latLimits[0] ) & (df['dropoff_latitude']  <= latLimits[1]) ]
df = df[(df['pickup_longitude']  >= longLimits[0]) & (df['pickup_longitude']  <= longLimits[1])]
df = df[(df['dropoff_longitude'] >= longLimits[0]) & (df['dropoff_longitude'] <= longLimits[1])]
df = df[(df['trip_duration']     >= durLimits[0] ) & (df['trip_duration']     <= durLimits[1]) ]
df = df.reset_index(drop=True)

allLat = np.array(list(df['pickup_latitude']) + 
                 list(df['dropoff_latitude']))
allLong = np.array(list(df['pickup_longitude']) +
                 list(df['dropoff_longitude']))

medianLat = np.percentile(allLat,50)
medianLong = np.percentile(allLong,50)

latMultiplier = 111.32
longMultiplier = np.cos(medianLat*(np.pi/180.0))*111.32

df['src lat [km]'] = latMultiplier*(df['pickup_latitude']-medianLat)
df['src long [km]'] = longMultiplier*(df['pickup_longitude']-medianLong)
df['dst lat [km]'] = latMultiplier*(df['dropoff_latitude']-medianLat)
df['dst long [km]'] = longMultiplier*(df['dropoff_longitude']-medianLong)
InÂ [3]:
allLat = np.array(list(df['src lat [km]'])+
                 list(df['dst lat [km]']))

                 list(df['dst long [km]']))

loc_df['long'] = allLong
loc_df['lat'] = allLat

plt.title('Clusters of New York')

fig,ax = plt.subplots(figsize = (10,10))
for label in loc_df.label.unique():
    ax.plot(loc_df.long[loc_df.label == label],loc_df.lat[loc_df.label == label],'.', alpha = 0.5, markersize = 0.5, color = 'gray')

    if trip_by_cluster['cluster'].loc[i]==0:
        color='r'
    elif trip_by_cluster['cluster'].loc[i]==1:
        color='g'
    #elif trip_by_cluster['cluster'].loc[i]==2:
    #    color='b'
    #else:
    #    color='y'
    plt.arrow(trip_by_cluster['src long [km]'].loc[i],
              trip_by_cluster['src lat [km]'].loc[i],
              trip_by_cluster['dst long [km]'].loc[i]-trip_by_cluster['src long [km]'].loc[i],
              trip_by_cluster['dst lat [km]'].loc[i]-trip_by_cluster['src lat [km]'].loc[i],
              head_width=0.2,
              length_includes_head=True,
              color=color,
              alpha=0.5
             )
plt.xlim([-4,5])
plt.ylim([-8,8])

plt.show()
